Feb 2024 Graph Theory Workshop Instructor

April 2024 - Sep 2024 Intelligence Intern | Stellar Solutions | Remote

May 2021 - Aug 2021 Shampoo Assistant | Salon Lofts | Sterling, VA

Single-handedly marketed and produced estimable Black and White portrait oil paintings
Analyzed proportions of individual facial features and backgrounds to recreate accurate representations on canvas
Committed over 40+ hours for each commissioned oil painting to refine technique and compose excellent product
